{"tid":1087562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我EQ低少少我應該殺撚左我老母","createTime":"2019-04-01T12:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T12:21:15.000Z","uid":245899,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a0c3618483ff8322fedcae150c4c100c69e975","tid":1087562,"uid":245899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:18:58.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打絲打啲屋企人好似我老母咁痴線<br />\n三日唔埋兩日發幾次脾氣<br />\n乜鳩都屌一餐<br />\n重點係每次都係無理取鬧<br />\n每次都攞翻十萬年前嘅嘢出嚟講<br />\n我老豆都怕撚左佢<br />\n<br />\n自問自己都算係咁 又冇反叛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話一就一 二就二 費撚事同佢嘈<br />\n打我我永遠唔還手<br />\n鬧我我永遠唔還口由得佢鬧<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以分享吓自己啲父母點對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇吓有冇人勁過我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28b10735ff420ad74b9a337cd71396a4a7658db","tid":1087562,"uid":146982,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"哦"}]}